<event name="RAD_LAB_QUEST_START" unique="true">
	<beaconType id="map_icon_rad_lab" global="true">
		<color r="146" g="232" b="228" a="1"/>
	</beaconType>
	<preventFleet />
	<quest>
		<nebulaBeacon>false</nebulaBeacon>
		<createNebula>false</createNebula>
		<nextSector>true</nextSector>
		<aggressive>2</aggressive>
	</quest>
	<ship load="SHIP_CIVILIAN_LAB" hostile="false"/>
	<text> You come across a strange laboratory. As soon as you arrive, it powers up what looks like a weapon, aimed right at your ship...</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Wait.</text>
		<event>e
			<text>The station immediately fires on you. You brace for impact.
			Just as it's about to hit the ship, a blinding flash of light hits you. Once your vision returns, you find yourself standing amongst a bunch of scientists in the middle of the station.
			
			A scientist is waiting for you. "Uh, sorry about contacting you this way. We just couldn't risk this information leaking out. Your ship is fine, by the way."
			The scientist gestures to the weapons console beside you. Your ship appears on the screen, unharmed.
			"Oh right, I'm Goose. I'm the head of this labratory. You're the renegade we've been hearing about, right?"</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Right.</text>
				<event>
					<text>"Excellent. We need your help with a certain issue regarding some rogue technology. However, we can't give you the details unless you're absolutly sure about helping."
					"Either way, feel free to browse our commercial technology, I'm sure someone like you could make use of it."</text>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>You'll help. [There are Multiple Possible Quests]</text>
						<event load="RAD_LAB_QUEST_LIST"/>
					</choice>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Sounds risky. Just shop.</text>
						<event>
							<text>"A shame, but understandable given the way you got here. Follow Duck over there to see our store of sorts."</text>
							<store>STORE_RADLAB</store>
						</event>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>You don't know what they want, but you aren't going to wait to see what happens. Attack!</text>
		<event>
			<text>You power up your weapons! The lab hails you: "You're making a mistake."</text>
			<ship hostile="true" />
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK" />
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

